Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥呢 遥怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你丢下了遥是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N\N重\N\N\N演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉的侵蚀变的严重起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空可能也会发生因果定律的审判
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 或许已经发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果定律的审判...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 究竟在说什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释的让我能明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指原因和结果逆转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因和结果逆转?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说过去要受到未来的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去要受到未来的影响?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的事情忘记了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说只是幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦才不是什么幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦一直在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备把龙之转矩怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年后的佑就是鸦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~已经七点半啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 早饭已经做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经8点多了哦 我要去上学了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第一学期最后的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是浮游灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和它说话了 就会被它拖进灵界去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像讨论的很热烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保的超常现象解说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃声已经响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回座位 回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假活动在班会结束以后再讨论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾 约会的日程都已经排满到三年后了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得稍微...有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下课时间 回家路上请小心）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这样就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原也要一起去哦 试胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为..为什么啊 试胆量什么的我才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我还有私塾 所以不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原 你可一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说藤原君是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的尿出来很丢人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你说什么 向井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做感觉很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那家伙 最近都不怎么合群了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤要参加中学考试的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虽然是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得稍微...有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艘好船吧 一艘就要两千五百亿日元呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不是客船 所以乘坐的感觉要差上那么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱原君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不也很想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约好了终止这项实验的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我没有说过要停止这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你不也接受了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是应该是正式的报酬...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我这边也付了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望至少要赚回我应得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里都是些光说不干的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在筑波的现场失败了三回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说5人都被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我已经没有关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要做的 就这样一直做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样再做下去只会让θ粒子分散掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在东京看实验的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让这个地域整个崩溃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 黛博士的女儿好像是住在这附近的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 我们一起来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越时间和空间的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去了佑的私塾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在私塾前面等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚还出来 会被绑架的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那么担心我 就不要离家出走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说要离家出走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你说想去东京的父亲那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候是和妈妈吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家父母又离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况很复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信以为真的我才是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑 不要生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算离家出走了 也只不过是很快就被找到带回家罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等成为大人了 什么地方都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 想快点变成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我变的不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 也不用推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 明天一起离家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约好了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要一起离家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去爸爸那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像...忘记了什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你爸爸联系上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是被说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为离家出走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离家出走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时空就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空是你所选择的时空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所选择的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然鸦是来自未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定是另一个佑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知什么时候鸦从我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为佑应该只有一个才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再一次..被遥救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战斗里 我应该死了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉到地面上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转到左边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行 前进的道路被妨碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦飞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过时空的狭缝所来到的就是这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我没有察觉到那个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我转移到了一个近似的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为被吸到了这个时空才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我转移到了这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库里玛才知道了这个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才知道了遥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还可能唤醒另一个时空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遥为目标...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了 要出来了 我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 向井 感觉很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 要与幽灵大人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加认真一些 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底祈祷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵大人 幽灵大人 请快快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没搞错吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在担心后藤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 他们家又不会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来哟 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 要跟不上美保他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我似乎忘记了一件非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 在见到幽灵之前决不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 有什么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 墓地里不应该没有幽灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么飞过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灵 是地缚灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 是冲着我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和这个时空的自己同化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了我的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 去了香格里拉你就会想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就是...你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是我该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我忘记了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在这里和鸦相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那之前见过鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春天即将来临的那个下雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空歪曲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你又来救我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没...没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.90,0:24:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.29,0:24:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我消失也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.94,0:24:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要和鸦战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.80,0:25:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就和我战斗吧 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.72,0:25:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能找到我自己吗

